place.name: WHITEKIRK
place.gazetteerText: Whitekirk and Tynninghame, coast par., Haddingtonshire, on river Tyne, 6195 ac., pop. 1051; the church is 4¼ miles SE. of North Berwick. (In 1887, John Bartholomew's Gazetteer of the British Isles)
